"Compare lump sum vs SIP investment strategies. SIPs help average out market volatility through rupee cost averaging." = "Compare lump sum vs SIP investment strategies. SIPs help average out market volatility through rupee cost averaging.";
"Keep a portion of your portfolio in Fixed Deposits for capital safety and guaranteed returns, especially for short-term goals." = "Keep a portion of your portfolio in Fixed Deposits for capital safety and guaranteed returns, especially for short-term goals.";
"Recurring Deposits help build financial discipline. Automate monthly savings to build a corpus over time." = "Recurring Deposits help build financial discipline. Automate monthly savings to build a corpus over time.";
"Use a Systematic Withdrawal Plan (SWP) to generate regular retirement income from your mutual fund investments." = "Use a Systematic Withdrawal Plan (SWP) to generate regular retirement income from your mutual fund investments.";
"Maximize your NPS contributions to get additional tax deductions under Section 80CCD(1B), over and above the 80C limit." = "Maximize your NPS contributions to get additional tax deductions under Section 80CCD(1B), over and above the 80C limit.";
"Track your Provident Fund balance regularly to plan for retirement. PF offers guaranteed returns with tax benefits." = "Track your Provident Fund balance regularly to plan for retirement. PF offers guaranteed returns with tax benefits.";

// MARK: - Tips & FAQ Long Descriptions (Loans)

"Try to maximize your down payment when taking a home loan. A higher down payment means lower EMIs and less interest paid overall." = "Try to maximize your down payment when taking a home loan. A higher down payment means lower EMIs and less interest paid overall.";
"Make prepayments on your home loan whenever possible. Even small additional payments can significantly reduce your total interest outgo." = "Make prepayments on your home loan whenever possible. Even small additional payments can significantly reduce your total interest outgo.";
"Avoid high-interest personal loans and credit card debt. Always compare interest rates and prefer secured loans for lower rates." = "Avoid high-interest personal loans and credit card debt. Always compare interest rates and prefer secured loans for lower rates.";
"No-cost EMI schemes often include hidden charges or inflated product prices. Always compare the total cost before opting for such plans." = "No-cost EMI schemes often include hidden charges or inflated product prices. Always compare the total cost before opting for such plans.";
"Always pay interest during the moratorium period of education loans. This prevents interest capitalization and reduces your total repayment." = "Always pay interest during the moratorium period of education loans. This prevents interest capitalization and reduces your total repayment.";
"Loan Against Property (LAP) typically offers lower interest rates than personal loans. Use it wisely for business or large expenses." = "Loan Against Property (LAP) typically offers lower interest rates than personal loans. Use it wisely for business or large expenses.";
"Understand the Loan-to-Value (LTV) ratio for gold loans. Lenders typically offer 75% of the gold's market value." = "Understand the Loan-to-Value (LTV) ratio for gold loans. Lenders typically offer 75% of the gold's market value.";

